{"tid":616174,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同啲成日要人擔心嘅女仔一齊真係好辛苦...","createTime":"2018-04-04T03:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T20:40:32.000Z","uid":10679,"like":40,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"70a9e692fd54c1fa60c5b7546a51059dd5b48cc3","tid":616174,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"都廿幾歲人啦，朝早返工前永遠唔食早餐，晚餐又唔定時食，放假可以懶落街而全日只食一餐。搞到成日胃痛，又唔睇醫生，睇完醫生叫佢去照胃鏡又唔去。<br />\n明知自己嚟m，又唔戒口，係咁飲凍嘢食雪糕食西瓜，跟住又話m痛痛到腰都痛埋...<br />\n放假約左幾點係邊到等，佢又唔見人，打電話又唔聽，上佢屋企拍門又冇人應，嚇鬼死以為咩事，隔幾個鐘打嚟話佢訓死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大個人都唔識照顧自己，但係成日係到呻話邊到痛 邊到唔舒服，成日要人擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e215ca3bfb73584870cf3845ac1978547d5259","tid":616174,"uid":126690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92cf95104105a74b300d3a65babbce722158747d","tid":616174,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"你遲早頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d07c2b8718ef14ba555d5e71f683d9fee185a41","tid":616174,"uid":155080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"飛"},{"pid":"834030daa927b60eda66b9729a94a68bc455e497","tid":616174,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"嗚嗚嗚"},{"pid":"ff35a926eee30ef0691b4ab8ec39289f240b5735","tid":616174,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"飛"},{"pid":"2adf7797ab3e724c2beca536c993b16d0606043d","tid":616174,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"你都頂得順"},{"pid":"265d8d6e2d5a66c81d699589d345b51cd21e13fc","tid":616174,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c62aea6b25e41fcd4b4171c98b5185479018021","tid":616174,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e481e7b5ad7d5e884c498536342d680b1277d50","tid":616174,"uid":61096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"我有個fd條女又係咁<br />\n成日唔錫身 乜都去盡 身體又唔好 又成日訓到消失左唔見人 有冇番屋企都唔知<br />\n都唔知佢點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18d9968add067eab93e35c4e36fefca5f5a42af","tid":616174,"uid":39394,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"上邊個兩段完全係我嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你啲語氣好似我男朋友<br />\n我一唔食野佢就會罵我唔識照顧自己<br />\n但唔知點解我覺得佢咁罵我好man<br />\n所以有時會專登話佢知我無食野搏罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c55e1b9bf4f4987019257d3b8de53655014cd5","tid":616174,"uid":25583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"我都想俾男朋友咁鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2a9f2fc74329ae78b49c09a41687819589ece9","tid":616174,"uid":81282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:15:40.000Z","msg":"我都想有人咁關心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c3d23d39af4e4c6748608de2902670afc47daa","tid":616174,"uid":170808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T20:40:32.000Z","msg":"分手啦"}]}